videos.description: Stanford quarterback K.J. Costello dumps a screen pass to Cameron Scarlett, who zips 46 yards to the end zone for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Scarlett jets to house for Stanford TD

videos.description: Stanford defensive back Paulson Adebo picks off Chase Garbers for the second time after hauling in a juggling interception.
videos.headline: Adebo intercepts Garbers again

videos.description: Cameron Scarlett's 3-yard touchdown puts a bow on Stanford's 23-13 win vs. California, his second of the game.
videos.headline: Scarlett punches in 2nd rush TD, ices game for Stanford
